name: NY IS HOWL
description:
HOWL! Art Around the Park 2013. I thought of everything I love and some things that I hate about NY. Based my designs on the iconic Milton Glaser "I love NY" logo. I filled in the heart with what New Yorkers love about this city. Check Instagram for more photos #nyis. 

This is original artwork and one of a kind art produced just for the HOWL! art festival. KRINK paint markers on white tarp material. 

Each NY IS square will be sold separately, unless a block is requested.  

I will Sign & Number each piece sold on the back.

While paying through PayPal, please let me know what square you want to purchase. You can do this by adding a note to seller under your shipping address. 

****

Missed out on the Square you wanted, contact me for commissioned work.

name: Artcrank poster
description: This was a poster I did for Artcrank NYC. Delivery bike gangs of New York. I have a couple left over from the show.

name: Timbrrr Beer Koozie
description:
These beauties are top quality neoprene beer koozies. Built to keep your Beer cold and your hands not cold. Cold beer is a Rose city right that everyone should have.

You get a pair (yes that is 2) of Timbrrr beer koozies. They are a foldable forest park green neoprene with white print. You can't find a more perfect stocking stuffer for your Timber fan this Christmas.
